values: no regrets-just lessons learned it feels good to finally be happy ♥
...always look at what you have left...never what you've lost...

driving in the car with michelle the other night after work, and she said the funniest thing i have ever heard. it is as follows: the song 'holiday inn' by chingy is on the radio, and this line of the song comes on "Then I thought about, no footage while I ram her" as michelle hears the "while I ram her" part she says "my entire vagina just cringed" and i have never laughed so hard in my entire life...hahahahahahhahahhha
